# Phase A2 rehearses the exact Phase A1 artifact that passed publication.
# Both image references are immutable multi-architecture OCI indexes.
# This is the exact multi-architecture index that created the bundled live
# volume before Phase A2b (PostgreSQL 16.14 / Alpine 3.23.4). Automatic
# existing-volume switches refuse every source artifact not rehearsed here.
